---
// Section 1 — Hero. The only section guaranteed to be read.
// Text-first (the call-screen mock is a later visual pass).
---

<section aria-labelledby="hero-title">
  <div class="mx-0 max-w-[720px] px-6 pt-10 pb-16 md:pl-20 md:pr-8 md:pt-16 md:pb-24">
    <h1 id="hero-title" class="font-display text-hero uppercase text-text-primary">
      Not real.<br />Still brutal.
    </h1>

    <p class="mt-8 max-w-[34ch] font-sans text-[22px] font-bold leading-tight text-text-primary md:text-[26px]">
      A phone call in English. With someone who hangs up on you.
    </p>

    <p class="mt-5 max-w-[46ch] text-body text-text-primary">
      Survive high-stakes calls with an AI that is sarcastic, impatient, and
      almost out of patience. Freeze, and it ends the call. Then it tells you
      exactly what you got wrong.
    </p>

    <p class="mt-4 max-w-[46ch] text-caption text-text-secondary">
      Spoken-English practice as a game you survive — not a study app.
    </p>

    <a
      href="#notify"
      class="mt-9 inline-block rounded-full bg-accent px-6 py-3 font-sans text-[15px] font-semibold text-bg"
    >
      Get notified
    </a>
  </div>
</section>
